**Testing Patterns**: Integration tests using supertest to make HTTP requests against routes
**Code Structure**: Routes-based organization with data module and types module
**No existing service layer**: All business logic is inline in route handlers
**Data Management**: In-memory arrays with manual ID management
**Middleware**: Basic express.json() middleware
**No existing models or database**: Uses TypeScript interfaces and in-memory data

