## Separation of Concerns Summary

| Concern | Route Handler | Service |
|---|---|---|
| Parse query/body params | ✅ | ❌ |
| Validate required HTTP fields (`userId`, `items`) | ✅ | ❌ |
| Validate body field types (`adjustment` is number, `status` is string) | ✅ | ❌ |
| Send HTTP status codes and JSON | ✅ | ❌ |
| Filter / search logic | ❌ | ✅ |
| Calculate derived fields (`isLowStock`, `inventoryValue`, `totalRevenue`) | ❌ | ✅ |
| Business validation (items > 0, stock sufficient, valid transition) | ❌ | ✅ |
| Mutate in-memory data | ❌ | ✅ |

